<P>
  <hr noshade size="1">
<H2>
  Attributes description
</H2>
<P>
The MirrorFrame defines the following attributes:
<UL>
  <LI>
    <A HREF="#mirrors">mirrors</A>
</UL>
<P>
  <hr noshade size="1">
<CODE><A NAME="mirrors">mirrors</A></CODE>
<DL>
  <DT>
    <I>semantics</I>
  <DD>
    The base URL of the site to mirror. This is typically of the form
    <B>http://host:port</B>, eg http://www.w3.org. 
  <DT>
    <I>type</I>
  <DD>
    This attribute is an editable
    <A HREF="http://jigsaw.w3.org/Doc/Programmer/api/org/w3c/tools/resources/StringAttribute.html">StringAttribute</A>
  <DT>
    <I>default value</I>
  <DD>
    This attribute defaults to <B>null</B>.
</DL>
<P>
